===Etymology===
First attested in 1831. From {{etyl|de|en}} {{m|de|Akkordeon}}, from {{m|de|Akkord||harmony}}, from {{der|en|fr|accord}}, from {{der|en|fro|acorder}}, based on {{der|en|it|accordare||to tune}}. See also [[accord]].

